short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Scrape web pages and upload them to Coze Knowledge
short.zh_CN: 采集网页内容并将其上传到扣子的知识库

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: When users are in Coze and try to create text online data units in the Knowledge, they can choose to manually annotate and scrape data by installing this extension.
long.zh_CN: 当用户在扣子中并尝试在知识库中创建文本在线数据单元时，可以通过安装此扩展程序来手动标注并采集数据。
